ISLAMABAD, Jan 12 (APP): Federal Minister for Maritime Affairs Ali Haider Zaidi on Tuesday said that as usual former Prime Minister Nawaz Sharif tried to buy his way out by offering a bribe to UK firm.
In a tweet, he said that like the rest of the world, Broadsheet CEO also considered Prime Minister Imran Khan to be a man of integrity.
